---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="護國息災萬人念佛" description="金剛護持會第十屆春季大愛共善救拔苦難護國息災萬人念佛，宸定精舍共同發起道場。">

  <!-- Banner -->
  <section class="page-banner" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0a00 0%, #3d1a00 50%, #1a0a00 100%); padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <p style="color:#c9a96e; letter-spacing:0.2em; font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">金剛護持會 · 第十屆春季</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.2rem; color:#fff; line-height:1.4; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">護國息災</h1>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.8rem; color:#c9a96e; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">萬人念佛</h1>
      <p style="color:#e8d5b0; font-size:1.1rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">大愛共善 · 救拔苦難</p>
      <p style="color:#c9a96e; font-size:1rem; margin-top:1rem;">2026 年 2 月 28 日 — 5 月 28 日</p>
      <p style="display:inline-block; background:#8b1a1a; color:#fff; padding:0.4rem 1.2rem; border-radius:2rem; font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:0.75rem;">報名截止：3 月 14 日（六）</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 活動緣起 -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">活動緣起</span>
        <h2>為何發起萬人念佛</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose" style="max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
        <blockquote style="border-left:4px solid #c9a96e; padding:1rem 1.5rem; background:#fdf8f0; margin:0 0 2rem 0; font-style:italic; color:#5a3e28; font-size:1.1rem;">
          「一切災難皆為眾生惡業所感，人人念佛，則此業可轉。」
          <footer style="margin-top:0.5rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:#8b6914;">—— 印光大師</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <p style="line-height:1.9; color:#4a3728;">
          此活動由十三處大道場共同發起，宸定精舍為共同發起道場之一。
          祈願國泰民安、風調雨順、世界和平、災疫不起、人心向善。
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:1.9; color:#4a3728; margin-top:1rem;">
          參加者，佛光注照、福壽綿長、身心康泰；
          病苦者，業消病癒、增福延壽；
          往生者，冀佛垂慈、得生安養。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 參加辦法 -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">參加辦法</span>
        <h2>如何參與念佛</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width:680px; margin:0 auto;">
        <div style="display:grid; gap:1.5rem;">
          <div class="card" style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="font-size:2rem; flex-shrink:0;">📿</div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.5rem 0;">持念聖號</h3>
              <p style="margin:0; color:#5a3e28;">持念【阿彌陀佛】聖號，居士以 <strong>20 萬遍</strong>為基本，法師隨喜。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="font-size:2rem; flex-shrink:0;">📅</div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.5rem 0;">圓滿期限</h3>
              <p style="margin:0; color:#5a3e28;">請於 <strong>5 月 28 日（四）前</strong>圓滿佛號，勿超過截止日。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; align-items:flex-start;">
            <div style="font-size:2rem; flex-shrink:0;">👨‍👩‍👧</div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.5rem 0;">代為報名</h3>
              <p style="margin:0; color:#5a3e28;">可代理親友、團體報名，廣結善緣，共沾法益。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; align-items:flex-start; background:#fff8f0; border:1px solid #e8c07a;">
            <div style="font-size:2rem; flex-shrink:0;">⚠️</div>
            <div>
              <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.5rem 0; color:#8b1a1a;">重要說明</h3>
              <p style="margin:0; color:#5a3e28;">報名後因統計上稟，故<strong>無法取消</strong>，請確認後再報名。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 圓滿法會 -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">圓滿法會</span>
        <h2>三時繫念暨祈福點燈法會</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:1.5rem; max-width:700px; margin:0 auto 2rem auto;">
        <div class="card" style="text-align:center; border-top:4px solid #c9a96e;">
          <p style="color:#8b6914; font-size:0.85rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">第一場次</p>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">春季圓滿法會</h3>
          <p style="font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:bold; color:#8b1a1a; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">3 月 28 日（六）</p>
          <p style="color:#5a3e28;">大慈山萬緣寺</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align:center; border-top:4px solid #c9a96e;">
          <p style="color:#8b6914; font-size:0.85rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">第二場次</p>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.3rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">夏季圓滿法會</h3>
          <p style="font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:bold; color:#8b1a1a; margin-bottom:0.25rem;">5 月 30 日（六）</p>
          <p style="color:#5a3e28;">大慈山萬緣寺</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose" style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
        <p style="color:#5a3e28; line-height:1.9;">
          特為每位報名者設立「消災牌位」與「超薦牌位」迴向。<br/>
          親自參加法會者，可於現場<strong>免費點燈</strong>。<br/>
          請於報名時先行告知參加場次。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 報名 -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">立即報名</span>
        <h2>報名截止 3 月 14 日</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width:700px; margin:0 auto;">
        <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:3rem;">
          <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">推薦使用線上表單報名，方便快速：</p>
          <a href="https://forms.gle/eVB9o3ZULzBnZhM17" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-gold" style="font-size:1.1rem; padding:0.9rem 2.5rem;">
            點此開啟線上報名表單
          </a>
        </div>
        <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:1.5rem;">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 style="color:#8b6914; border-bottom:1px solid #e8d5b0; padding-bottom:0.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🧑‍⚖️ 法師報名窗口</h3>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
              <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0;">張美麗 居士</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0.25rem 0;">LINE：yao_mama2017</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0;">📞 0919-203-475</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0;">李雪清 居士</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0.25rem 0;">LINE：0960419886</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0;">📞 0939-148-420</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 style="color:#8b6914; border-bottom:1px solid #e8d5b0; padding-bottom:0.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🙏 居士報名窗口</h3>
            <div style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
              <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0;">周道 學長</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0.25rem 0;">LINE：0937170085</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0;">📞 0937-170-085</p>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
              <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0;">邱寶娟 學長</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0.25rem 0;">LINE：0931237082</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0;">📞 0931-237-082</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p style="font-weight:bold; margin:0;">林麗明 學長</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0.25rem 0;">LINE：ming1284</p>
              <p style="color:#5a3e28; margin:0;">📞 0958-066-621</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 發起道場 -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">共同發起</span>
        <h2>十三處大道場聯合護持</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
        <p style="color:#5a3e28; line-height:2; font-size:1rem;">
          埔里圓通寺・圓通寺分院杭內觀音寺<br/>
          大慈山萬緣寺及六大分院<br/>
          內湖恆光禪寺・華嚴禪寺・西印禪寺<br/>
          <strong style="color:#8b1a1a; font-size:1.1rem;">宸定精舍</strong>・吉祥精舍<br/>
          及其他共同發起道場，合計十三處
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:2rem; color:#8b6914; font-style:italic;">金剛護持會 合十敬白</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 返回活動 -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="/activities" class="btn btn-outline">← 返回所有活動</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>